Background tasks using runners like codex, claude code, opencode, etc, should have their sessions tracked so that we can resume and reprompt them. We will need to check these tools --help and maybe search online for how to detect their session id. All runners should be implemented using a common framework that ensures they support all necessary features like getting sesison ids and the like.
